# Doxxy - Clinic Management App - Project Structure

## Root Directory Structure
```
clinic-life-orchestrator/
├── .cursor/                  # Cursor IDE configuration
├── .git/                     # Git repository
├── dist/                     # Build output directory
├── node_modules/             # Node.js dependencies
├── public/                   # Static assets
├── src/                      # Source code
├── supabase/                 # Supabase configuration and migrations
├── .gitignore               # Git ignore rules
├── components.json          # Shadcn UI components configuration
├── development-log.md       # Development progress and changes
├── eslint.config.js         # ESLint configuration
├── index.html              # Entry HTML file
├── package.json            # Project dependencies and scripts
├── postcss.config.js       # PostCSS configuration
├── README.md               # Project documentation
├── tailwind.config.ts      # Tailwind CSS configuration
├── tsconfig.json           # TypeScript configuration
├── tsconfig.app.json       # TypeScript app configuration
├── tsconfig.node.json      # TypeScript Node configuration
└── vite.config.ts          # Vite configuration
```

## Source Code Structure (`src/`)
```
src/
├── components/             # Reusable UI components
├── contexts/              # React context providers
├── hooks/                 # Custom React hooks
├── integrations/          # Third-party service integrations
├── lib/                   # Utility functions and shared code
├── pages/                 # Page components
├── types/                 # TypeScript type definitions
├── App.css               # Main application styles
├── App.tsx               # Root application component
├── index.css             # Global styles
├── main.tsx              # Application entry point
└── vite-env.d.ts         # Vite environment type definitions
```

## Key Features and Components

### Authentication & User Management
- Google OAuth integration
- Role-based access control (superadmin, staff, doctor)
- Profile completion flow
- Member invitation system

### Clinic Management
- Multi-tenant architecture
- Department management
- Member management
- Clinic settings

### Patient Care
- Patient profiles
- Medical records
- Appointments
- Consultations

### Billing
- Bill creation and management
- Payment tracking
- Status monitoring

### UI/UX
- Modern React with TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for styling
- Shadcn UI components
- Responsive design
- Toast notifications

### Backend & Infrastructure
- Supabase for database and authentication
- Edge Functions for serverless operations
- Row-Level Security (RLS) policies
- Environment-based configuration

### Development Tools
- ESLint for code quality
- Prettier for code formatting
- TypeScript for type safety
- Vite for build tooling
- React Query for data fetching
- Zod for form validation

## Database Schema
The database schema is managed through Supabase migrations in the `supabase/` directory. Key tables include:
- profiles
- clinics
- departments
- members
- patients
- appointments
- consultations
- medical_records
- bills

## Security
- Row-Level Security (RLS) policies
- Role-based access control
- Secure authentication flows
- Environment variable management
- API key protection 